  "texts": [
    "We also identify the potential areas of application for TLP using the framework.",
    "To demonstrate its practical applications, we apply it to technical text data from MWOs of aircraft and identify two relevant scenarios of application.",
    "We first use the existing data from the MWOs to help in predicting corrective actions for new maintenance problems.",
    "We identify existing maintenance problems using both syntactic and semantic textual similarity techniques and predict the top three corrective actions for new maintenance problems based on cosine similarity scores.",
    "We use text similarity methods because the data lacks any form of annotation to allow classification models to be used, and maintenance problems do not necessarily have a true corrective action."
  ],
